    "originContent": "Deploy a Hytale dedicated server with a community-focused Docker image by 10+ contributors. This project simplifies Hytale self-hosting with built-in security, networking and debugging tools. Join our active Discord for direct support and to connect with other server owners. Whether you're testing mods or running a persistent world, this container provides a consistent, production-ready environment in one command.",
    "translatedContent": "Deploy a Hytale dedicated server with a community-focused Docker image by 10+ contributors. This project simplifies Hytale self-hosting with built-in security, networking and debugging tools. Join our active Discord for direct support and to connect with other server owners. Whether you're testing mods or running a persistent world, this container provides a consistent, production-ready environment in one command."
